abstract: The prototype, developed by Toyota and Tesla Motors at remarkable speed, indicates that each company is learning from the other.
snippet: The prototype, developed by Toyota and Tesla Motors at remarkable speed, indicates that each company is learning from the other.
lead_paragraph: It was over glasses of red wine on a May evening in Palo Alto, Calif., that Akio Toyoda, president of Toyota, and Elon Musk, founder of the electric vehicle start-up company Tesla Motors, first talked through the particulars of a partnership they had just announced.

headline.main: Unlikely Alliance Results in an All-Electric RAV4
headline.print_headline: An Unlikely Alliance Quickly Results in an All-Electric RAV4
